Change the Chart Type

Switch between chart types to see which visualization options tell the most compelling story for your data.

While viewing data in a lens, tap View. A gallery of chart types appears. You can slide the lower portion of the window up to see more chart types, and down to see your chart. Select a chart type. The chart visualization changes to match your selection.
